{"tid":849216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"火炭明渠變螢光河！","createTime":"2018-10-05T13:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T14:02:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2225fbdaa578a2c69c8966e4070e794e4da808","tid":849216,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538739506_14bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538739506_14bc.jpg&h=8aeeb636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火炭工業區附近有渠道被染成螢光綠色，讀者高先生向《蘋果》表示，今天在火炭站附近，目睹渠道整條變成螢光綠色，「今日先係咁，成條渠都係綠色，好似仲慢慢流咗入城門河」。<br />\n<br />\n環保署回覆指，今日上午接獲市民投訴後，已派員到現場巡查，確定螢光的源頭，來自火炭一工業大廈，該工廈今早用螢光色粉，測試天台防漏，初步調查結果顯示，螢光不含有毒物質，且可生物降解，相關的螢光顏色會逐漸消散。<br />\n<br />\n署方表示，已抽取水樣本及要求有關承辦商提供螢光粉的資料，作進一步調查。渠務署亦表示已派員到場視察。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538739970_e47a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538739970_e47a.jpg&h=b8b4c72d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"909469af2e9824f36619508d3e8df2df30ade563","tid":849216,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"又幾靚喎"},{"pid":"206c19efa340f3fd863a450da97af77e29131f04","tid":849216,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:50:05.000Z","msg":"接軌"},{"pid":"597d8704e8cbb822ec1559db083bedb303259392","tid":849216,"uid":11254,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wVXQQcU7N8A/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FwVXQQcU7N8A%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=95350a8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0771ec3fa29d54189de12a9e1b30898bde504a97","tid":849216,"uid":102702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"